sub_title: MD PhD Global Health & Tropical Medicine | iSTEPup
summary: Global health oriented doctor striving for equal changes in the world especially in terms of healthcare & education. Strong believer of local capacity building, increasing self-reliance and research driven medical care. Knows well how to improvise and work in resource constrained settings. Interested in health systems, public health, family medicine, education and sustainability.
